15. Implementation Roadmap

Phase 1 — Manual forge
	•	define schemas
	•	create 20–50 core nodes
	•	add explicit edges
	•	add 10–20 transfer rules
	•	validate by hand

Phase 2 — Query layer
	•	alias search
	•	invariant match
	•	neighborhood expansion
	•	simple similarity ranking

Phase 3 — Canon discipline
	•	promotion / deprecation workflow
	•	fossilization of stale nodes
	•	version tracking

Phase 4 — Spectral analysis
	•	graph clustering
	•	bridge-node detection
	•	doctrine attractor mapping

